ad towards other districts later. Risk of flash-flood  especially at low-lying and flood prone areas. Wind gust of up to 50km/h is possible in heavy and thundery showers.</div></td></tr><tr style='height:19px;'><th id="137659748R5" style="height: 19px;" class="row-headers-background row-header-shim"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 19px;">6</div></th><td class="s0">16/12/2015</td><td class="s1">Several areas in the Brunei Muara District will experience water supply disruption and low water pressure especially in high areas today from 9 in the evening. </td></tr><tr style='height:19px;'><th id="137659748R6" style="height: 19px;" class="row-headers-background row-header-shim"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 19px;">7</div></th><td class="s0">16/12/2015</td><td class="s2 softmerge"><div class="softmerge-inner" style="width: 1842px; left: -1px;">Following Typhoon Melor that is currently sweeping through the Philippines, Brunei Darussalam has the potential to experience active weather starting tomorrow until the 19th of this month with chances of occasional showers or thundershowers.</div></td></tr><tr style='height:19px;'><th id="137659748R7" style="height: 19px;" class="row-headers-background row-header-shim"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 19px;">8</div></th><td class="s0">16/12/2015</td><td class="s1">Brunei Darussalam will be experiencing heavy-rain in the next few days due to Typhoon Melor</td></tr><tr style='height:19px;'><th id="137659748R8" style="height: 19px;" class="row-headers-background row-header-shim"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 19px;">9</div></th><td class="s0">16/12/2015</td><td class="s1">Brunei&#39;s neighboring country, Philippines, have been swept by Typhoon Melor in which this country will experience heavy-rainstorms due to the typhoon</td></tr><tr style='height:19px;'><th id="137659748R9" style="height: 19px;" class="row-headers-background row-header-shim"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 19px;">10</div></th><td class="s0">16/12/2015</td><td class="s1">heavy rainfall for two days already</td></tr><tr style='height:19px;'><th id="137659748R10" style="height: 19px;" class="row-headers-background row-header-shim"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 19px;">11</div></th><td class="s0">16/12/2015</td><td class="s1">Yellow Stage Weather Warning. </td></tr><tr style='height:19px;'><th id="137659748R11" style="height: 19px;" class="row-headers-background row-header-shim"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 19px;">12</div></th><td class="s0">16/12/2015</td><td class="s1">heavy rainfall for straight two days</td></tr><tr style='height:19px;'><th id="137659748R12" style="height: 19px;" class="row-headers-background row-header-shim"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 19px;">13</div></th><td class="s0">16/12/2015</td><td class="s1">Safely landed at Miri... Now on the way back to Brunei... However heavy traffic &amp; raining all the way…</td></tr><tr style='height:19px;'><th id="137659748R13" style="height: 19px;" class="row-headers-background row-header-shim"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 19px;">14</div></th><td class="s0">17/12/2015</td><td class="s1">heavy rain be alert of flood due to continuous-rain</td></tr><tr style='height:19px;'><th id="137659748R14" style="height: 19px;" class="row-headers-background row-header-shim"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 19px;">15</div></th><td class="s0">17/12/2015</td><td class="s1">Always be careful on the road, especially during the heavy-rain.</td></tr><tr style='height:19px;'><th id="137659748R15" style="height: 19px;" class="row-headers-background row-header-shim"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 19px;">16</div></th><td class="s0">17/12/2015</td><td class="s1">like water village already due to heavy rainfall</td></tr><tr style='height:19px;'><th id="137659748R16" style="height: 19px;" class="row-headers-background row-header-shim"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 19px;">17</div></th><td class="s0">17/12/2015</td><td class="s1">heavy-rain in continuous-rain predicted flash-flood for few hours</td></tr><tr style='height:19px;'><th id="137659748R17" style="height: 19px;" class="row-headers-background row-header-shim"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 19px;">18</div></th><td class="s0">17/12/2015</td><td class="s1">Always be careful when driving in the rain. The road is slippery. There has been numerous number of accidents reported. Avoid it before it’s too late.</td></tr><tr style='height:19px;'><th id="137659748R18" style="height: 19px;" class="row-headers-background row-header-shim"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 19px;">19</div></th><td class="s0">17/12/2015</td><td class="s1">To all the road users out there to always be aware when driving on the road during a heavy-rain. Don’t speed as your carelessness might endanger other road users. The roads are slippery during a heavy-rain.</td></tr><tr style='height:19px;'><th id="137659748R19" style="height: 19px;" class="row-headers-background row-header-shim"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 19px;">20</div></th><td class="s0">17/12/2015</td><td class="s1">Don’t drive during the rain. Wait for it to deter. You can always watch Star Wars whilst waiting for the heavy-rain to subside.</td></tr><tr style='height:19px;'><th id="137659748R20" style="height: 19px;" class="row-headers-background row-header-shim"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 19px;">21</div></th><td class="s0">17/12/2015</td><td class="s1">Heavy-rain at night… the white lines are invisible during a heavy-rain.</td></tr><tr style='height:19px;'><th id="137659748R21" style="height: 19px;" class="row-headers-background row-header-shim"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 19px;">22</div></th><td class="s0">17/12/2015</td><td class="s1">heavy-rain in continuous-rain predicted flash-flood for few hours</td></tr><tr style='height:19px;'><th id="137659748R22" style="height: 19px;" class="row-headers-background row-header-shim"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 19px;">23</div></th><td class="s0">17/12/2015</td><td class="s1">becareful due to heavy rainfall at Negara Brunei Darussalam..when there is any accident please report to here so we can get any updated news on traffic, hopefully there wont any accident happen from this disaster</td></tr><tr style='height:19px;'><th id="137659748R23" style="height: 19px;" class="row-headers-background row-header-shim"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 19px;">24</div></th><td class="s0">17/12/2015</td><td class="s1">The Police of Sengkurong received a call at 11.50am about a car accident driven by a man that happened along the way of Jalan Jerudong to Jalan Tutong. Fortunately, no injuries were reported.</td></tr><tr style='height:19px;'><th id="137659748R24" style="height: 19px;" class="row-headers-background row-header-shim"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 19px;">25</div></th><td class="s0">17/12/2015</td><td class="s1">The Police Department has advised the public to always take steps that they have to take to avoid any accidents during this uncertain weather.</td></tr><tr style='height:19px;'><th id="137659748R25" style="height: 19px;" class="row-headers-background row-header-shim"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 19px;">26</div></th><td class="s0">17/12/2015</td><td class="s1">where is it?</td></tr><tr style='height:19px;'><th id="137659748R26" style="height: 19px;" class="row-headers-background row-header-shim"><div class="row-header-wrapper" style="line-height: 19px;">27</div></th><td class="s0">17/12/2015</td><td class="s1">in the past I would loved when heavy rainfall that causes flash floods so that I can escape for going to school, at the present I rather flash flood wi